ault Shadow'=>'网格卡片默认阴影','Grid Card Hover Scale'=>'网格卡片悬停缩放','Lightbox'=>'灯箱','Transition Duration (ms)'=>'过渡持续时间 (ms)','Backdrop Color'=>'背景颜色','Entry Scale'=>'进入缩放','Video Max Width'=>'视频最大宽度','Video Height'=>'视频高度','Media Max Height'=>'媒体最大高度','CSS value, e.g. 85vh'=>'CSS 值，例如 85vh','Z-Index'=>'Z 轴层级','Navigation'=>'导航','Max Visible Dots'=>'最多可见圆点数','Arrow Edge Inset (px)'=>'箭头边缘内嵌 (px)','Arrow Min Hit Target (px)'=>'箭头最小点击目标 (px)','Arrow Fade Duration (ms)'=>'箭头淡出持续时间 (ms)','Arrow Scale Transition (ms)'=>'箭头缩放过渡 (ms)','Viewport Height Mobile Ratio'=>'视口高度移动比例','Viewport Height Tablet Ratio'=>'视口高度平板比例','Search Input Min Width (px)'=>'搜索输入框最小宽度 (px)','Search Input Max Width (px)'=>'搜索输入框最大宽度 (px)','System'=>'系统','Admin Search Debounce (ms)'=>'管理搜索防抖 (ms)','Min Password Length'=>'最小密码长度','Login Form Max Width (px)'=>'登录表单最大宽度 (px)','Developer & Debugging'=>'开发者与调试','Enable Component Debug Names & Markers'=>'启用组件调试名称和标记','When enabled, deployed builds keep explicit React DevTools component names and inject data-wpsg-component/data-wpsg-slot attributes into the DOM for Elements inspection and QA selectors. Local dev may still show source component names even when this is off.'=>'启用后，已部署的构建会保留明确的 React DevTools 组件名称，并将 data-wpsg-component/data-wpsg-slot 属性注入到 DOM 中，用于元素检查和 QA 选择器。即使关闭此项，本地开发环境仍可能显示源组件名称。','Data Maintenance'=>'数据维护','Archive Purge After (days)'=>'归档清除时间（天）','Archived campaigns older than this are moved to trash. Set to 0 to disable automatic purging.'=>'超过此时长的已归档活动将被移至回收站。设为 0 以禁用自动清除。','Trash Grace Period (days)'=>'回收站宽限期（天）','Trashed campaigns are permanently deleted after this many days. Minimum 7 days.'=>'回收站中的活动将在这么多天后被永久删除。最少 7 天。','Analytics Retention (days)'=>'分析数据保留（天）','Analytics events older than this are purged weekly. Set to 0 to keep indefinitely.'=>'超过此时长的分析事件将每周清除。设为 0 则无限期保留。','Object Cache'=>'对象缓存','Health data unavailable'=>'健康数据不可用','Could not load object-cache status from the server.'=>'无法从服务器加载对象缓存状态。','Persistent cache'=>'持久缓存','Not detected'=>'未检测到','No persistent object cache'=>'无持久对象缓存','WordPress is using its default in-memory cache, which is discarded on every request. For higher-traffic deployments consider adding a Redis or Memcached drop-in. See docs/object-cache-setup.md for setup instructions.'=>'WordPress 正在使用其默认的内存缓存，该缓存会在每次请求时被丢弃。对于流量较高的部署，请考虑添加 Redis 或 Memcached drop-in。有关设置说明，请参阅 docs/object-cache-setup.md。','Cache backend detected but no runtime stats are exposed by this drop-in.'=>'已检测到缓存后端，但此 drop-in 未公开运行时统计信息。','Backend stats'=>'后端统计','Danger Zone'=>'危险区域','Irreversible data deletion'=>'不可逆的数据删除','When preservation is disabled, deleting this plugin permanently removes all campaigns, layout templates, overlay library, analytics events, access grants, and uploaded thumbnail files. This cannot be undone.'=>'禁用保留后，删除此插件将永久移除所有活动、布局模板、叠加层库、分析事件、访问授权和已上传的缩略图文件。此操作无法撤销。','Preserve data on plugin removal'=>'移除插件时保留数据','When enabled (recommended), all plugin data is kept if you remove the plugin. Disable only if you intend to wipe all gallery data on uninstall.'=>'启用后（推荐），如果您移除插件，所有插件数据都会保留。仅当您打算在卸载时清除所有图库数据时才禁用。','{{base}} — Override for {{bp}}'=>'{{base}} — {{bp}} 的覆盖','{{base}} — Inherited from {{bp}}'=>'{{base}} — 继承自 {{bp}}','↻ Reset to inherited'=>'↻ 重置为继承','Card Appearance'=>'卡片外观','Border Radius'=>'边框圆角','Corner rounding for campaign cards'=>'活动卡片的圆角','Border Width (px)'=>'边框宽度 (px)','Left accent border thickness'=>'左侧强调边框粗细','Border Color Mode'=>'边框颜色模式','How card accent border colors are determined'=>'如何确定卡片强调边框颜色','Single color for all cards'=>'所有卡片使用单一颜色','Per-card color (set in Edit Campaign)'=>'每张卡片单独设置颜色（在“编辑活动”中设置）','Border Color'=>'边框颜色','Accent border color applied to all campaign cards'=>'应用于所有活动卡片的强调边框颜色','Card Shadow'=>'卡片阴影','Depth effect for campaign cards'=>'活动卡片的深度效果','Subtle'=>'轻微','Medium'=>'中等','Dramatic'=>'强烈','Thumbnail Height'=>'缩略图高度','Height of the card thumbnail area'=>'卡片缩略图区域的高度','Thumbnail Fit'=>'缩略图适应','How the thumbnail image fills the card'=>'缩略图如何填充卡片','Cover (fill)'=>'覆盖（填充）','Contain (fit)'=>'包含（适应）','Element Visibility'=>'元素可见性','Show company name badge'=>'显示公司名称徽章','Company badge overlay on card thumbnail'=>'卡片缩略图上的公司徽章叠加层','Show access badge'=>'显示访问徽章','Green \'Access\' badge on accessible cards'=>'可访问卡片上的绿色“访问”徽章','Show card title'=>'显示卡片标题','Show the campaign title in the card info panel'=>'在卡片信息面板中显示活动标题','Show card description'=>'显示卡片描述','Show the campaign description in the card info panel'=>'在卡片信息面板中显示活动描述','Show media counts'=>'显示媒体数量','Video and image count below description'=>'描述下方的视频和图片数量','Show card border'=>'显示卡片边框','Accent border and hover border effect'=>'强调边框和悬停边框效果','Show thumbnail fade'=>'显示缩略图渐变','Gradient overlay at bottom of thumbnail'=>'缩略图底部的渐变叠加层','Show card info panel'=>'显示卡片信息面板','Show title, description, tags & media counts below thumbnail'=>'在缩略图下方显示标题、描述、标签和媒体数量','Card Grid & Pagination'=>'卡片网格与分页','Cards Per Row'=>'每行卡片数','Number of columns in the card grid (Auto = responsive)'=>'卡片网格中的列数（自动 = 响应式）','Auto (responsive)'=>'自动（响应式）','2 columns'=>'2 列','3 columns'=>'3 列','4 columns'=>'4 列','5 columns'=>'5 列','6 columns'=>'6 列','Max Columns (auto mode)'=>'最大列数（自动模式）','Cap the number of columns when using Auto layout. 0 = unlimited.'=>'使用自动布局时限制列数。0 = 无限制。','Horizontal Gap'=>'水平间距','Horizontal spacing between campaign cards'=>'活动卡片之间的水平间距','Vertical Gap'=>'垂直间距','Vertical spacing between campaign card rows'=>'活动卡片行之间的垂直间距','Card Max Width'=>'卡片最大宽度','Limit individual card width. 0 = no limit (fill column).'=>'限制单张卡片的宽度。0 = 无限制（填充列）。','Card Scale'=>'卡片缩放','Primary sizing multiplier for cards. 1 = default size.'=>'卡片的主要尺寸倍数。1 = 默认大小。','Card Justification'=>'卡片对齐方式','How cards distribute when a row does not fill the full available width.'=>'当一行未填满全部可用宽度时卡片如何分布。','Start'=>'起始','Center'=>'居中','End'=>'末尾','Space Between'=>'两端对齐','Space Evenly'=>'均匀分布','Vertical Alignment'=>'垂直对齐','How the card grid aligns vertically when minimum height exceeds content height.'=>'当最小高度超过内容高度时卡片网格如何垂直对齐。','Top'=>'顶部','Bottom'=>'底部','Grid Minimum Height'=>'网格最小高度','Minimum height for the card grid container.'=>'卡片网格容器的最小高度。','Grid Maximum Height'=>'网格最大高度','Maximum height for the card grid area. 0 = no limit.'=>'卡片网格区域的最大高度。0 = 无限制。','Grid Horizontal Offset'=>'网格水平偏移','Fine-tune horizontal position of the card grid.'=>'微调卡片网格的水平位置。','Grid Vertical Offset'=>'网格垂直偏移','Fine-tune vertical position of the card grid.'=>'微调卡片网格的垂直位置。','Card Aspect Ratio'=>'卡片宽高比','Lock cards to a fixed aspect ratio'=>'将卡片锁定为固定宽高比','Auto (natural)'=>'自动（自然）','16:9 (widescreen)'=>'16:9（宽屏）','4:3 (standard)'=>'4:3（标准）','1:1 (square)'=>'1:1（正方形）','3:4 (portrait)'=>'3:4（竖向）','9:16 (tall portrait)'=>'9:16（高竖向）','2:3 (photo portrait)'=>'2:3（照片竖向）','3:2 (photo landscape)'=>'3:2（照片横向）','21:9 (ultrawide)'=>'21:9（超宽）','Card Min Height'=>'卡片最小高度','Minimum height for each card. 0 = no minimum.'=>'每张卡片的最小高度。0 = 无最小值。','Pagination'=>'分页','Display Mode'=>'显示模式','How cards are displayed: all at once, progressively loaded, or paginated with arrows'=>'卡片的显示方式：一次全部显示、逐步加载或使用箭头分页','Show All'=>'显示全部','Load More (progressive)'=>'加载更多（逐步）','Paginated (arrows)'=>'分页（箭头）','Rows Per Page'=>'每页行数','Number of card rows visible per page'=>'每页可见的卡片行数','Dot Navigator'=>'圆点导航器','Show dot navigator below the card grid'=>'在卡片网格下方显示圆点导航器','Page Transition Duration (ms)'=>'页面过渡持续时间 (ms)','Slide animation speed between pages'=>'页面之间的滑动动画速度','Card Internals'=>'卡片内部','Locked Card Opacity'=>'锁定卡片不透明度','Gradient Start Opacity'=>'渐变起始不透明度','Gradient End Opacity'=>'渐变结束不透明度','Lock Icon Size (px)'=>'锁定图标大小 (px)','Size of the lock icon shown on inaccessible cards'=>'在不可访问卡片上显示的锁定图标大小','Access Icon Size (px)'=>'访问图标大小 (px)','Size of the icon inside the access badge'=>'访问徽章内图标的大小','Badge Offset Y (px)'=>'徽章 Y 偏移 (px)','Vertical offset from the top edge for access and company badges'=>'访问徽章和公司徽章相对于顶部边缘的垂直偏移','Company Badge Max Width (px)'=>'公司徽章最大宽度 (px)','Maximum width of the company badge before truncation'=>'公司徽章截断前的最大宽度','Thu