','Padding inside the modal content area (clamped 0-48).'=>'窗口内容区域内的内边距（限制在 0-48）。','Modal Appearance'=>'窗口外观','Cover Image Height'=>'封面图片高度','Height of the cover image in the campaign modal'=>'活动窗口中封面图片的高度','Modal Transition'=>'窗口过渡','Animation style when opening the campaign modal'=>'打开活动窗口时的动画样式','Pop (scale up)'=>'弹出（放大）','Slide Up'=>'向上滑动','Modal Transition Duration (ms)'=>'窗口过渡持续时间 (ms)','Length of the modal open/close animation'=>'窗口打开/关闭动画的时长','Modal Max Height (vh%)'=>'窗口最大高度 (vh%)','Maximum height of the campaign modal as a percentage of viewport (clamped 50-95).'=>'活动窗口的最大高度，以视口的百分比表示（限制在 50-95）。','Content Visibility'=>'内容可见性','Show Company Name'=>'显示公司名称','Show the company badge on the campaign cover image.'=>'在活动封面图片上显示公司徽章。','Show Date'=>'显示日期','Show the creation date under the campaign title.'=>'在活动标题下方显示创建日期。','Show About Section'=>'显示关于部分','Show the "About this Campaign" heading and description.'=>'显示“关于此活动”标题和描述。','About Section Heading'=>'关于部分标题','Heading for the campaign description section (default "About").'=>'活动描述部分的标题（默认“关于”）。','Show Description'=>'显示描述','Show the campaign description text within the About section.'=>'在关于部分内显示活动描述文本。','Show Campaign Stats'=>'显示活动统计','Show the statistics block (video count, image count, tags, visibility).'=>'显示统计块（视频数量、图片数量、标签、可见性）。','Stats Admin-Only'=>'统计仅限管理员','When enabled, only admins can see the statistics block.'=>'启用后，只有管理员可以查看统计块。','Show Cover Image'=>'显示封面图片','Show the campaign cover image at the top of the viewer.'=>'在查看器顶部显示活动封面图片。','Show Tags'=>'显示标签','Show tags section in the campaign viewer.'=>'在活动查看器中显示标签部分。','Show Admin Actions'=>'显示管理操作','Show admin action buttons (edit, archive, etc.) in the campaign viewer.'=>'在活动查看器中显示管理操作按钮（编辑、归档等）。','Show Gallery Labels'=>'显示图库标签','Show \'Images\' and \'Videos\' heading labels above galleries in the viewer.'=>'在查看器中图库上方显示“图片”和“视频”标题标签。','Gallery Labels'=>'图库标签','Image Gallery Label'=>'图片图库标签','Custom label for image gallery sections. Count is appended automatically.'=>'图片图库部分的自定义标签。数量会自动附加。','Video Gallery Label'=>'视频图库标签','Custom label for video gallery sections. Count is appended automatically.'=>'视频图库部分的自定义标签。数量会自动附加。','Label Justification'=>'标签对齐方式','Horizontal alignment for gallery section labels'=>'图库部分标签的水平对齐','Left'=>'左','Right'=>'右','Show Gallery Label Icon'=>'显示图库标签图标','Display an icon prefix before each gallery section label'=>'在每个图库部分标签前显示图标前缀','Modal Background'=>'窗口背景','Modal Background Type'=>'窗口背景类型','Background style for the fullscreen campaign modal'=>'全屏活动窗口的背景样式','Modal Background Color'=>'窗口背景颜色','Solid background color for the fullscreen modal'=>'全屏窗口的纯色背景颜色','Cover Image & Responsive'=>'封面图片与响应式','Cover Mobile Ratio'=>'封面移动比例','Cover Tablet Ratio'=>'封面平板比例','Close Button Size (px)'=>'关闭按钮大小 (px)','Close Button Background'=>'关闭按钮背景','CSS color for the close button background (e.g. rgba(0,0,0,0.5)).'=>'关闭按钮背景的 CSS 颜色（例如 rgba(0,0,0,0.5)）。','Mobile Breakpoint (px)'=>'移动断点 (px)','Viewport width below which the campaign viewer switches to mobile layout.'=>'活动查看器在此视口宽度以下切换到移动布局。','Description Line Height'=>'描述行高','Viewport & Layout'=>'视口与布局','Enable Lightbox'=>'启用灯箱','Enable fullscreen lightbox when clicking gallery items.'=>'单击图库项时启用全屏灯箱。','Enable Animations'=>'启用动画','Enable smooth animations and transitions. Disable for better performance on low-end devices.'=>'启用流畅的动画和过渡。在低端设备上禁用可获得更好的性能。','Viewport Dimensions'=>'视口尺寸','Height Constraint'=>'高度约束','Choose whether classic galleries can overflow, are kept within the visible screen, or use a manual CSS height.'=>'选择经典图库是可以溢出、保持在可见屏幕内，还是使用手动 CSS 高度。','No restraint'=>'无约束','Restrain to view'=>'限制在视图内','Manually control height'=>'手动控制高度','Manual Gallery Height'=>'手动图库高度','Accepted units: px, em, rem, vh, dvh, vw, %. Example: 75vh or 420px'=>'可接受的单位：px、em、rem、vh、dvh、vw、%。示例：75vh 或 420px','Image Border Radius'=>'图片边框圆角','Corner rounding for image gallery viewport and thumbnails.'=>'图片图库视口和缩略图的圆角。','Video Border Radius'=>'视频边框圆角','Corner rounding for video gallery viewport and thumbnails.'=>'视频图库视口和缩略图的圆角。','Shadow & Depth'=>'阴影与深度','Image Shadow Preset'=>'图片阴影预设','Box-shadow depth effect for image gallery viewport.'=>'图片图库视口的盒阴影深度效果。','Strong'=>'强','Custom'=>'自定义','Image Custom Shadow'=>'图片自定义阴影','CSS box-shadow value (e.g. \'0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)\').'=>'CSS 盒阴影值（例如“0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)”）。','Video Shadow Preset'=>'视频阴影预设','Box-shadow depth effect for video gallery viewport.'=>'视频图库视口的盒阴影深度效果。','Video Custom Shadow'=>'视频自定义阴影','Tile Appearance'=>'图块外观','Gap X'=>'间距 X','Horizontal gap between tiles.'=>'图块之间的水平间距。','Gap Y'=>'间距 Y','Vertical gap between tile rows.'=>'图块行之间的垂直间距。','Tile border thickness. 0 = no border.'=>'图块边框粗细。0 = 无边框。','Hover Bounce'=>'悬停弹跳','Scale-up spring animation when hovering over a tile.'=>'悬停在图块上时的放大弹簧动画。','Hover Glow'=>'悬停发光','Drop-shadow glow on hover (works with clip-path shapes).'=>'悬停时的投影发光（适用于 clip-path 形状）。','Glow Color'=>'发光颜色','Glow Spread (px)'=>'发光扩散 (px)','Radius of the glow effect.'=>'发光效果的半径。','Transitions'=>'过渡','Transition Fade'=>'过渡淡入淡出','Apply an opacity fade when cards enter and exit during transitions, softening abrupt edges.'=>'在过渡期间卡片进入和退出时应用不透明度淡入淡出，柔化突兀的边缘。','Transition Type'=>'过渡类型','How gallery media slides between items: fade only, slide only, or combined slide-fade.'=>'图库媒体在项之间切换的方式：仅淡入淡出、仅滑动或滑动淡入淡出组合。','Slide + Fade'=>'滑动 + 淡入淡出','Scroll Animation Style'=>'滚动动画样式','Navigation scroll behavior for gallery thumbnail strips.'=>'图库缩略图条的导航滚动行为。','Smooth'=>'平滑','Instant'=>'即时','Animation Duration (ms)'=>'动画持续时间 (ms)','Duration for gallery transition and thumbnail highlight animations.'=>'图库过渡和缩略图高亮动画的持续时间。','Animation Easing'=>'动画缓动','Timing function used for gallery transitions.'=>'用于图库过渡的计时函数。','Ease'=>'缓动 (ease)','Linear'=>'线性','Ease In'=>'缓入','Ease Out'=>'缓出','Ease In Out'=>'缓入缓出','Thumbnail Strip'=>'缩略图条','Video Thumb Width (px)'=>'视频缩略图宽度 (px)','Width of video thumbnail items.'=>'视频缩略图项的宽度。','Video Thumb Height (px)'=>'视频缩略图高度 (px)','Height of video thumbnail items.'=>'视频缩略图项的高度。','Image Thumb Width (px)'=>'图片缩略图宽度 (px)','Width of image thumbnail items.'=>'图片缩略图项的宽度。','Image Thumb Height (px)'=>'图片缩略图高度 (px)','Height of image thumbnail items.'=>'图片缩略图项的高度。','Thumbnail Gap (px)'=>'缩略图间距 (px)','Spacing between thumbnail items in the strip.'=>'条中缩略图项之间的间距。','Wheel Scroll'=>'滚轮滚动','Allow mouse wheel to scroll the thumbnail strip horizontally.'=>'允许鼠标滚轮水平滚动缩略图条。','Drag Scroll'=>'拖动滚动','Allow click-and-drag to scroll the thumbnail strip.'=>'允许单击并拖动来滚动缩略图条。','Strip Scroll Buttons'=>'条滚动按钮','Show left/right scroll buttons on the thumbnail strip edges.'=>'在缩略图条边缘显示左/右滚动按钮。','Thumbnail Scroll Speed'=>'缩略图滚动速度','Multiplier for thumbnail-strip wheel scroll speed.'=>'缩略图条滚轮滚动速度的倍数。','Overlay Arrows'=>'叠加箭头','Arrow Vertical Position'=>'箭头垂直位置','Vertical alignment of the overlay prev/next arrows.'=>'叠加的上一个/下一个箭头的垂直对齐。','Arrow Size (px)'=>'箭头大小 (px)','Diameter of the overlay navigation arrows.'=>'叠加导航箭头的直径。','Arrow Color'=>'箭头颜色','Icon color for the overlay arrows.'=>'叠加箭头的图标颜色。','Arrow Background Color'=>'箭头背景颜色','Background color (supports rgba for transparency).'=>'背景颜色（支持 rgba 实现透明度）。','Arrow Border Width (px)'=>'箭头边框宽度 (px)','Border thickness around the arrows (0 = none).'=>'箭头周围的边框粗细（0 = 无）。','Hover Scale Factor'=>'悬停缩放系数','Auto-hide Delay (ms)'=>'自动隐藏延迟 (ms)','Show arrows on hover/interaction. 0 = always visible.'=>'在悬停/交互时显示箭头。0 = 始终可见。','Enable Dot Navigator'=>'启用圆点导航器','Show a dot-style page indicator.'=>'显示圆点式页面指示器。','Dot Position'=>'圆点位置','Where to render the dot navigator relative to the viewport.'=>'圆点导航器相对于视口的渲染位置。','Below Viewport'=>'视口下方','Overlay Bottom'=>'叠加底部','Overlay Top'=>'叠加顶部','Dot Size (px)'=>'圆点大小 (px)','Diameter of each dot.'=>'每个圆点的直径。','Dot Shape'=>'圆点形状','Shape of the navigation dots.'=>'导航圆点的形状。','Circle'=>'圆形','Pill'=>'胶囊形','Square'=>'方形','Active Dot Color'=>'活动圆点颜色','Color for the currently active dot (CSS value).'=>'当前活动圆点的颜色（CSS 值）。','Inactive Dot Color'=>'非活动圆点颜色','Color for inactive dots (CSS value).'=>'非活动圆点的颜色（CSS 值）。','Dot Spacing (px)'=>'圆点间距 (px)','Gap between dots.'=>'圆点之间的间距。','Active Dot Scale'=>'活动圆点缩放','Carousel Settings'=>'轮播设置','Visible Cards'=>'可见卡片数','Number of slides visible at once in the carousel.'=>'轮播中一次可见的幻灯片数量。','Slide Gap'=>'幻灯片间距','Space between carousel slides.'=>'轮播幻灯片之间的间距。','Loop'=>'循环','Continuously loop slides when reaching the end.'=>'到达末尾时连续循环幻灯片。','Drag Enabled'=>'启用拖动','Allow dragging/swiping to navigate slides.'=>'允许拖动/滑动来浏览幻灯片。','Autoplay'=>'自动播放','Automatically advance slides.'=>'自动切换幻灯片。','Autoplay Speed (ms)'=>'自动播放速度 (ms)','Delay between automatic slide transitions.'=>'自动幻灯片过渡之间的延迟。','Pause on Hover'=>'悬停时暂停','Pause autoplay when the mouse hovers over the carousel.'=>'当鼠标悬停在轮播上时暂停自动播放。','Autoplay Direction'=>'自动播放方向','Direction autoplay advances slides.'=>'自动播放切换幻灯片的方向。','Left to Right'=>'从左到右','Right to Left'=>'从右到左','Visual Effects'=>'视觉效果','Darken Unfocused Slides'=>'使未聚焦的幻灯片变暗','Apply a dark overlay on slides that are not currently selected.'=>'在当前未选中的幻灯片上应用深色叠加层。','Darken Opacity'=>'变暗不透明度','Opacity of the darken overlay (0 = transparent, 1 = fully dark).'=>'变暗叠加层的不透明度（0 = 透明，1 = 完全变暗）。','Edge Fade'=>'边缘淡化','Fade slides at the edges of the carousel viewport.'=>'在轮播视口的边缘淡化幻灯片。','Section Sizing & Spacing'=>'部分尺寸与间距','Gallery Section Max Width'=>'图库部分最大宽度','Maximum width for each gallery section. 0 = fill available space.'=>'每个图库部分的最大宽度。0 = 填充可用空间。','Gallery Section Min Width'=>'图库部分最小宽度','Minimum width floor for gallery sections.'=>'图库部分的最小宽度下限。','Section Height Mode'=>'部分高度模式','How section height is determined. Auto = content-driven (recommended for masonry/justified).'=>'部分高度的确定方式。自动 = 由内容驱动（推荐用于瀑布流/两端对齐）。','Auto (content-driven)'=>'自动（内容驱动）','Manual (fixed max height)'=>'手动（固定最大高度）','Viewport (% of screen)'=>'视口（屏幕百分比）','Gallery Section Max Height'=>'图库部分最大高度','Maximum height for gallery sections in manual mode.'=>'手动模式下图库部分的最大高度。','Gallery Section Min Height'=>'图库部分最小高度','Minimum height floor for gallery sections.'=>'图库部分的最小高度下限。','Section Scale'=>'部分缩放','Primary sizing multiplier for gallery sections. Scales min/max width, min/max height, and padding proportionally. 1 = default size.'=>'图库部分的主要尺寸倍数。按比例缩放最小/最大宽度、最小/最大高度和内边距。1 = 默认大小。','Section Content Alignment'=>'部分内容对齐','Content Horizontal Alignment'=>'内容水平对齐','Horizontal alignment of adapter content within each gallery section.'=>'每个图库部分内适配器内容的水平对齐。','Content Vertical Alignment'=>'内容垂直对齐','Vertical alignment of adapter content within each gallery section.'=>'每个图库部分内适配器内容的垂直对齐。','Content Horizontal Offset'=>'内容水平偏移','Fine-tune horizontal position of section content. Negative = left, positive = right.'=>'微调部分内容的水平位置。负值 = 左，正值 = 右。','Content Vertical Offset'=>'内容垂直偏移','Fine-tune vertical position of section content. Negative = up, positive = down.'=>'微调部分内容的垂直位置。负值 = 上，正值 = 下。','Equal Height Sections (Per-Type)'=>'等高部分（按类型）','When using per-type galleries, display image and video sections side-by-side at equal height on tablet+ viewports.'=>'使用按类型图库时，在平板及更大视口上以等高并排显示图片和视频部分。','Gallery Section Padding'=>'图库部分内边距','Inner padding within each gallery section wrapper.'=>'每个图库部分包装器内的内边距。','Adapter Content Padding'=>'适配器内容内边距','Inner padding within each adapter (gallery grid). 0 = edges meet section boundary.'=>'每个适配器（图库网格）内的内边距。0 = 边缘与部分边界相接。','Vertical alignment of content within the modal.'=>'窗口内内容的垂直对齐。','Gallery Spacing'=>'图库间距','Gallery Shell Vertical Alignment'=>'图库外壳垂直对齐','Vertical alignment of the gallery sections within the viewer shell.'=>'查看器外壳内图库部分的垂直对齐。','Gallery Shell Vertical Offset'=>'图库外壳垂直偏移','Fine-tune vertical position of the gallery sections. Negative = up, positive = down.'=>'微调图库部分的垂直位置。负值 = 上，正值 = 下。','Gallery Max Width'=>'图库最大宽度','Maximum width of the gallery container. 0 = full responsive width.'=>'图库容器的最大宽度。0 = 完整响应式宽度。','Gallery Section Gap'=>'图库部分间距','Vertical gap between gallery sections.'=>'图库部分之间的垂直间距。','Gallery Edge Margin'=>'图库边缘外边距','Horizontal margin on gallery edges.'=>'图库边缘的水平外边距。','Adapter Sizing'=>'适配器尺寸','Adapter Sizing Mode'=>'适配器尺寸模式','How adapters fill their gallery section. Fill = 100% of section, Manual = custom percentage.'=>'适配器如何填充其图库部分。填充 = 部分的 100%，手动 = 自定义百分比。','Fill (100%)'=>'填充（100%）','Manual (custom %)'=>'手动（自定义 %）','Adapter Max Width (%)'=>'适配器最大宽度 (%)','Adapter width as percentage of its gallery section.'=>'适配器宽度占其图库部分的百分比。','Adapter Max Height (%)'=>'适配器最大高度 (%)','Adapter height as percentage of its gallery section.'=>'适配器高度占其图库部分的百分比。','Adapter Item Gap'=>'适配器项间距','Spacing between items in grid adapters (Compact Grid). 0 = no gap.'=>'网格适配器（紧凑网格）中项之间的间距。0 = 无间距。','Adapter Justification'=>'适配器对齐方式','How adapter items distribute within the container (Compact Grid, Circular).'=>'适配器项在容器内的分布方式（紧凑网格、环形）。','Stretch'=>'拉伸','Item Scale'=>'项缩放','Primary sizing multiplier for gallery items. Scales card width/height (Compact Grid), row height (Justified), and tile size (Shape adapters) proportionally. 1 = default size. Does not apply to Carousel.'=>'图库项的主要尺寸倍数。按比例缩放卡片宽度/高度（紧凑网格）、行高（两端对齐）和图块大小（形状适配器）。1 = 默认大小。不适用于轮播。','Solid Color'=>'纯色','Gradient'=>'渐变','Background Image'=>'背景图片','Solid background color behind the viewport'=>'视口后面的纯色背景颜色','Background Gradient'=>'背景渐变','CSS gradient string used behind the viewport'=>'视口后面使用的 CSS 渐变字符串','Background Image URL'=>'背景图片 URL','Image shown behind the viewport'=>'视口后面显示的图片','Viewport Backgrounds'=>'视口背景','Image Gallery Background'=>'图片图库背景','Background applied behind image gallery viewports'=>'应用于图片图库视口后面的背景','Video Gallery Background'=>'视频图库背景','Background applied behind video gallery viewports'=>'应用于视频图库视口后面的背景','Unified Gallery Background'=>'统一图库背景','Background applied when unified gallery mode is active'=>'统一图库模式激活时应用的背景','Drag scroll'=>'拖动滚动','Infinite scroll'=>'无限滚动','Keyboard nav'=>'键盘导航','Touch swipe'=>'触摸滑动','Layout builder'=>'布局构建器','Listing'=>'列表','Reset to default'=>'重置为默认','Reset {{label}} to default'=>'将 {{label}} 重置为默认','Enter a value between {{min}} and {{max}}'=>'输入介于 {{min}} 和 {{max}} 之间的值','Value exceeds maximum of {{max}}'=>'值超过最大值 {{max}}','Stored value "{{value}}" is not a valid option'=>'存储的值“{{value}}”不是有效的选项','Unified Gallery Mode'=>'统一图库模式','When enabled, images and videos are combined in a single gallery view. When disabled, each media type uses its own layout independently.'=>'启用后，图片和视频合并在单个图库视图中。禁用后，每种媒体类型独立使用自己的布局。','Choose the unified gallery adapter used at each breakpoint.'=>'选择每个断点使用的统一图库适配器。','Some adapters are unavailable on mobile — they require a larger screen (shown greyed out above).'=>'某些适配器在移动设备上不可用 — 它们需要更大的屏幕（上方显示为灰色）。','Choose separate image and video adapters for each breakpoint.'=>'为每个断点选择单独的图片和视频适配器。','Breakpoint Pixel Thresholds'=>'断点像素阈值','Width thresholds (px) used by the classic carousel adapter to determine the active breakpoint. Defaults match Mantine (768 / 1200).'=>'经典轮播适配器用于确定活动断点的宽度阈值 (px)。默认值与 Mantine 一致（768 / 1200）。','Mobile max (px)'=>'移动最大值 (px)','Max container width considered mobile. (320–1440, default: 768)'=>'视为移动的最大容器宽度。（320–1440，默认：768）','Enter a value between 320 and 1440'=>'输入介于 320 和 1440 之间的值','Mobile threshold must be less than tablet threshold'=>'移动阈值必须小于平板阈值','Tablet max (px)'=>'平板最大值 (px)','Max container width considered tablet. (320–1920, default: 1200)'=>'视为平板的最大容器宽度。（320–1920，默认：1200）','Enter a value between 320 and 1920'=>'输入介于 320 和 1920 之间的值','Tablet threshold must be greater than mobile threshold'=>'平板阈值必须大于移动阈值','Exports adapter configuration and carousel/media settings. Global navigation, breakpoint, and presentation settings are not included.'=>'导出适配器配置和轮播/媒体设置。不包括全局导航、断点和呈现设置。','Export adapter settings'=>'导出适配器设置','Import adapter settings'=>'导入适配器设置','Reset all adapter settings to defaults'=>'将所有适配器设置重置为默认','Gallery Adapters'=>'图库适配器','Quick breakpoint selectors stay inline here. Use the responsive editor when you need shared layout settings, adapter-specific fields, or deeper nested config changes.'=>'快速断点选择器保留在此处的内联位置。当您需要共享布局设置、适配器专用字段或更深层的嵌套配置更改时，请使用响应式编辑器。','Desktop edits the base card settings. Tablet and mobile can override selected layout and appearance fields without changing the desktop baseline.'=>'桌面编辑基础卡片设置。平板和移动可以覆盖选定的布局和外观字段，而不更改桌面基线。','Card settings breakpoint'=>'卡片设置断点','— None (use inline HTML fallback) —'=>'— 无（使用内联 HTML 回退）—','Page #{{id}}'=>'页面 #{{id}}','Access Request Magic-Link'=>'访问请求魔法链接','When an admin clicks a one-click approval link, the result is shown on this page (via '=>'当管理员单击一键批准链接时，结果会显示在此页面上（通过 ','). If no page is selected, a minimal inline HTML page is returned instead.'=>'）。如果未选择页面，则会改为返回一个最小的内联 HTML 页面。','Magic-link landing page'=>'魔法链接登录页','Loading pages…'=>'正在加载页面…','Select a page'=>'选择一个页面','Customize fonts, sizes, colors, and effects for individual text elements. Empty fields use theme defaults.'=>'为各个文本元素自定义字体、大小、颜色和效果。空字段使用主题默认值。','Element Overrides'=>'元素覆盖','Reset all typography'=>'重置所有排版','Viewer Title'=>'查看器标题','Viewer Subtitle'=>'查看器副标题','Card Title'=>'卡片标题','Card Description'=>'卡片描述','Card Company Name'=>'卡片公司名称','Card Media Counts'=>'卡片媒体数量','Campaign Title'=>'活动标题','Campaign Description'=>'活动描述','Campaign Date'=>'活动日期','Campaign About Heading'=>'活动关于标题','Campaign Stats Value'=>'活动统计值','Campaign Stats Label'=>'活动统计标签','Gallery Label'=>'图库标签','Media Caption'=>'媒体标题','Auth Bar Text'=>'认证栏文本','Access Badge Text'=>'访问徽章文本','Rounded-corner radius for image media surfaces in supported adapters.'=>'受支持适配器中图片媒体表面的圆角半径。','Rounded-corner radius for video media surfaces in supported adapters.'=>'受支持适配器中视频媒体表面的圆角半径。','Space between items in justified and masonry gallery layouts.'=>'两端对齐和瀑布流图库布局中项之间的间距。','Tile border thickness. Set 0 to disable borders.'=>'图块边框粗细。设为 0 以禁用边框。','CSS color used for tile borders when border width is greater than 0.'=>'当边框宽度大于 0 时用于图块边框的 CSS 颜色。','#ffffff'=>'#ffffff','Drop-shadow glow on hover for supported tile-based adapters.'=>'受支持的基于图块的适配器在悬停时的投影发光。','CSS color used for the hover glow effect.'=>'用于悬停发光效果的 CSS 颜色。','#7c9ef8'=>'#7c9ef8','Image Viewport Height'=>'图片视口高度','Base height used for image-dominant classic galleries before breakpoint scaling. Manual gallery height overrides this when the shared height mode is set to manual.'=>'在断点缩放之前用于以图片为主的经典图库的基础高度。当共享高度模式设为手动时，手动图库高度会覆盖此项。','Video Viewport Height'=>'视频视口高度','Base height used for video-dominant classic galleries before breakpoint scaling. Manual gallery height overrides this when the shared height mode is set to manual.'=>'在断点缩放之前用于以视频为主的经典图库的基础高度。当共享高度模式设为手动时，手动图库高度会覆盖此项。','Box-shadow depth effect for image-dominant classic galleries.'=>'以图片为主的经典图库的盒阴影深度效果。','CSS box-shadow value used when the image shadow preset is custom.'=>'当图片阴影预设为自定义时使用的 CSS 盒阴影值。','0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)'=>'0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)','Box-shadow depth effect for video-dominant classic galleries.'=>'以视频为主的经典图库的盒阴影深度效果。','CSS box-shadow value used when the video shadow preset is custom.'=>'当视频阴影预设为自定义时使用的 CSS 盒阴影值。','Allow dragging or swiping to navigate slides.'=>'允许拖动或滑动来浏览幻灯片。','Foreground color used for the overlay arrow icon and border.'=>'用于叠加箭头图标和边框的前景色。','Background fill applied behind the overlay arrows.'=>'应用于叠加箭头后面的背景填充。','rgba(0,0,0,0.45)'=>'rgba(0,0,0,0.45)','Scale factor applied when hovering the overlay arrows.'=>'悬停叠加箭头时应用的缩放系数。','Show arrows on hover or interaction. 0 keeps them always visible.'=>'在悬停或交互时显示箭头。0 使其始终可见。','Distance between the overlay arrows and the carousel edge.'=>'叠加箭头与轮播边缘之间的距离。','Minimum touch and click target size for the overlay arrows.'=>'叠加箭头的最小触摸和单击目标大小。','Fade-in and fade-out duration used when arrows auto-hide.'=>'箭头自动隐藏时使用的淡入和淡出持续时间。','Hover-scale transition duration for the overlay arrows.'=>'叠加箭头的悬停缩放过渡持续时间。','Maximum number of dot buttons shown before truncation inserts ellipses.'=>'在截断插入省略号之前显示的圆点按钮的最大数量。','Fill color used for the active dot.'=>'用于活动圆点的填充颜色。','var(--wpsg-color-primary)'=>'var(--wpsg-color-primary)','Fill color used for inactive dots.'=>'用于非活动圆点的填充颜色。','rgba(128,128,128,0.4)'=>'rgba(128,128,128,0.4)','Scale multiplier applied to the active dot.'=>'应用于活动圆点的缩放倍数。','Fraction of the viewport height reserved for the carousel on mobile.'=>'在移动设备上为轮播保留的视口高度比例。','Fraction of the viewport height reserved for the carousel on tablet.'=>'在平板上为轮播保留的视口高度比例。','Card Width'=>'卡片宽度','Primary width target for each compact-grid card. The grid wraps responsively around this width.'=>'每张紧凑网格卡片的主要目标宽度。网格会围绕此宽度进行响应式换行。','Locks card proportions without requiring a separate height control. Auto keeps legacy height-derived behavior.'=>'锁定卡片比例，无需单独的高度控制。自动保留旧版基于高度的行为。','Auto (legacy height-derived)'=>'自动（旧版，基于高度）','5:7 (playing card)'=>'5:7（扑克牌）','Max Columns (0 = auto)'=>'最大列数（0 = 自动）','Caps the number of compact-grid columns while preserving responsive wrapping.'=>'在保留响应式换行的同时限制紧凑网格列数。','Card Min Height (px)'=>'卡片最小高度 (px)','Optional guard that prevents extremely thin cards on narrow containers. Set 0 to disable.'=>'可选保护，防止在窄容器上出现极薄的卡片。设为 0 以禁用。','Target Row Height (px)'=>'目标行高 (px)','Ideal pixel height for each justified row. This is an algorithm input for react-photo-album, not a CSS value.'=>'每个两端对齐行的理想像素高度。这是 react-photo-album 的算法输入，而非 CSS 值。','Photo Normalize Height (px)'=>'照片归一化高度 (px)','Normalization pixel height for aspect-ratio scaling before layout. Lower values produce smaller tiles.'=>'布局前用于宽高比缩放的归一化像素高度。较低的值会产生较小的图块。','Masonry Columns (0 = auto)'=>'瀑布流列数（0 = 自动）','Number of masonry columns. Set 0 to let the layout choose responsively (1-4 based on width).'=>'瀑布流列数。设为 0 让布局响应式选择（根据宽度为 1-4）。','Auto Column Breakpoints'=>'自动列断点','Comma-separated width:columns pairs used when masonry columns are set to auto.'=>'当瀑布流列数设为自动时使用的以逗号分隔的宽度:列数对。','480:2,768:3,1024:4,1280:5'=>'480:2,768:3,1024:4,1280:5','Entrance Animation'=>'进入动画','Optional first-render animation for Masonry tiles. \'Waterfall\' staggers each tile into view from below. Respects prefers-reduced-motion.'=>'瀑布流图块的可选首次渲染动画。“瀑布”让每个图块从下方错开进入视图。遵循 prefers-reduced-motion。','Waterfall (stagger in)'=>'瀑布（错开进入）','Entrance Stagger (ms)'=>'进入错开 (ms)','Delay in milliseconds between successive tile animations in Waterfall mode.'=>'瀑布模式下连续图块动画之间的延迟（毫秒）。','Hero Aspect Ratio'=>'主图宽高比','Fixed aspect ratio of the hero display area.'=>'主图显示区域的固定宽高比。','Thumbnail Size'=>'缩略图大小','Width and height of each thumbnail strip item.'=>'每个缩略图条项的宽度和高度。','Duration of the hero swap and thumbnail highlight transitions.'=>'主图切换和缩略图高亮过渡的持续时间。','Strip Position'=>'条位置','Position of the thumbnail strip. \'Right\' falls back to \'Below\' on narrow containers.'=>'缩略图条的位置。在窄容器上，“右侧”会回退到“下方”。','Below'=>'下方','Right (wide containers)'=>'右侧（宽容器）','Hero Max Width'=>'主图最大宽度','Maximum width of the spotlight layout. Set 0 to disable (full container width).'=>'聚光灯布局的最大宽度。设为 0 以禁用（完整容器宽度）。','Hero Justification'=>'主图对齐方式','Horizontal alignment of the hero block within the container when Hero Max Width makes it narrower than the container.'=>'当主图最大宽度使其比容器更窄时，主图块在容器内的水平对齐。','Start (left)'=>'起始（左）','End (right)'=>'末尾（右）','Snap Alignment'=>'吸附对齐','CSS scroll-snap-align value applied to each slide. Controls where each slide snaps relative to the scroll container.'=>'应用于每张幻灯片的 CSS scroll-snap-align 值。控制每张幻灯片相对于滚动容器的吸附位置。','Page Indicator'=>'页面指示器','Show a slide counter (n / total) in the lower-right corner of each slide.'=>'在每张幻灯片的右下角显示幻灯片计数器（n / 总数）。','Container Max Width'=>'容器最大宽度','Maximum width of the scroll-snap container. Set 0 to disable (full container width).'=>'滚动吸附容器的最大宽度。设为 0 以禁用（完整容器宽度）。','Tile Size'=>'图块大小','Width and height of each shape tile (unified gallery).'=>'每个形状图块的宽度和高度（统一图库）。','Image Tile Size'=>'图片图块大小','Shape tile size for the image gallery.'=>'图片图库的形状图块大小。','Video Tile Size'=>'视频图块大小','Shape tile size for the video gallery.'=>'视频图库的形状图块大小。','Horizontal gap between shape tiles.'=>'形状图块之间的水平间距。','Vertical gap between shape-tile rows.'=>'形状图块行之间的垂直间距。','Layout Builder Scope'=>'布局构建器范围','Full: replaces entire gallery (no thumbnail strip). Viewport: replaces only the viewport area.'=>'完整：替换整个图库（无缩略图条）。视口：仅替换视口区域。','Full Gallery'=>'完整图库','Viewp